                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-24-defend201 t17980704-24-punish111"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, <rs id="t17980704-24-punish112" type="punishmentDescription">
