                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-24-defend201 t17980704-24-punish112"></join>
               publicly whipped
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
